<BodyLayout title="About">
  <p>
    Lions Club of Bangalore Prerana is a part of Lions Clubs International,
    charted in March 2022 by Lion Sowmya B. A. as its charter president.
  </p><p>
    The club was chartered with a team of 21 members who aspire to serve the
    less fortunate within the local community and to maintain a clean and green
    environment.
  </p><p>
    The focus areas of the team are environment, health, education, empowering
    women and children with skill-based training programs and care for the aged
    and disabled.
  </p>
